  },
  "primaryContentSections": [
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can preview localizations early in development while you lay out your app’s interface",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "for both SwiftUI and Interface Builder apps. For SwiftUI apps, you need to add the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "language or import the localization before you preview it, described in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/adding-support-for-languages-and-regions",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "and ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.Xcode/documentation/Xcode/importing-localizations",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ". For Interface Builder apps, you can first preview",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "the interface in pseudolanguages and then later in the localizations you add.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Add-localizations-to-a-SwiftUI-preview",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Add localizations to a SwiftUI preview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For SwiftUI apps, you can preview a localization by setting the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/SwiftUI/EnvironmentValues/locale",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "environment variable in your code. Use the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/SwiftUI/View/environment(_:_:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "function to set the locale for all views in the view hierarchy of a SwiftUI preview.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "For example, if you add German to your project, you can set the locale to German",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "(",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "de",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": "):",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code": [
            "struct ContentView_Previews: PreviewProvider {",
            "    static var previews: some View {",
            "        ContentView()",
            "                .environment(\\.locale, .init(identifier: \"de\"))",
            "    }",
            "}"
          ],
          "syntax": "swift",
          "type": "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To preview right-to-left languages, also set the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/SwiftUI/EnvironmentValues/layoutDirection",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "key to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/SwiftUI/LayoutDirection/rightToLeft",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To preview multiple localizations, add additional previews to your code and set the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/SwiftUI/EnvironmentValues/locale",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " environment",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "value for each. The localizations appear in the SwiftUI preview.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "previewing-localizations-1",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor": "Preview-localizations-in-Interface-Builder",
          "level": 3,
          "text": "Preview localizations in Interface Builder",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "For Interface Builder, you can preview localizations any time during development",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "by choosing localizations including pseudolanguages in the preview. You don’t need",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to build and run your app to see the preview.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In Interface Builder, select the desired view controller. Click the Adjust Editor",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Options button in the upper-right corner, then choose Preview. A preview of the layout",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "appears to the right of the canvas.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "In the preview area, select a preview or click in the background to deselect all",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "previews. If you don’t select a preview, you’ll change the language of all previews.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Click the language button—for example, English—in the lower-right corner. In the",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "pop-up menu that appears, choose a localization or pseudolanguage.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "identifier": "previewing-localizations-2",
              "type": "image"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
